     1 IDENTIFICATION  DIVISION.
     2 PROGRAM-ID.     EXERC1.
     3 AUTHOR.         YHAGO PESSOA.
     4 INSTALLATION.   FATEC-SP.
     5 DATE-WRITTEN.   25/02/2025.
     6 DATE-COMPILED. 24-Apr-25 22:01.
     7 SECURITY. APENAS O AUTOR PODE MODIFICA-LO.
     8
     9 ENVIRONMENT     DIVISION.
    10 CONFIGURATION SECTION.
    11 SOURCE-COMPUTER.  MY-PC.
    12 OBJECT-COMPUTER.  MY-PC.
    13 SPECIAL-NAMES.    DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA.
    14
    15 INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
    16 FILE-CONTROL.
    17     SELECT   CADSOC1     ASSIGN      TO       DISK
    18     ORGANIZATION  IS         LINE        SEQUENTIAL.
    19     SELECT   CADSOC2     ASSIGN     TO       DISK
    20     ORGANIZATION  IS         LINE        SEQUENTIAL.
    21     SELECT RELSOCIO      ASSIGN      TO       DISK.
    22
    23 DATA           DIVISION.
    24 FILE SECTION.
    25
    26 FD  CADSOC1
    27     LABEL   RECORD  STANDARD
    28     VALUE    OF FILE-ID    IS         "CAD-ENT.DAT".
    29 01  REG-ENT.
    30     02 CODIGOPAGAMENTO1   PIC 9(02).
    31     02 NUMEROSOCIO1       PIC 9(06).
    32     02 NOMESOCIO1         PIC X(30).
    33     02 VALORPAGAMENTO1    PIC 9(09)V9(02).
    34
    35 FD  CADSOC2
    36     LABEL   RECORD  STANDARD
    37     VALUE   OF FILE-ID    IS   "CAD-SAI.DAT".
    38 01  REG-SAI.
    39     02 NUMERO-SOCIO2        PIC 9(06).
    40     02 NOME-SOCIO2          PIC X(30).
    41     02 VALOR-PAGAMENTO2     PIC 9(09)V9(02).
    42
    43 FD  RELSOCIO
    44     LABEL RECORD IS OMITTED.
    45 01 REG-ATR      PIC X(80).
    46
    47 WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
    48     77 FIM-ARQ      PIC X(03)    VALUE "NAO".
    49     77 CT-LIN       PIC 9(02) VALUE 30.
    50     77 CT-PAG       PIC 9(02) VALUE ZEROS.
    51     77 SOMA-SOCIO   PIC 9(05) VALUE ZEROS.
    52     77 SOMA-VALOR  PIC 9(12)V99 VALUE ZEROS.
    53 01 PAG.
    54     02 FILLER     PIC X(70) VALUE SPACES.
    55     02 FILLER     PIC X(05) VALUE "PAG. ".
    56     02 VAR-PAG    PIC 99.
    57     02 FILLER     PIC X(03) VALUE SPACES.
* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 24-Apr-25 22:01 Page   2
*                                      EXERC1.CBL
    58 01 CAB-01.
    59     02 FILLER     PIC X(26) VALUE SPACES.
    60     02 FILLER     PIC X(27) VALUE "RELAÇĂO DE SÓCIOS ATRASADOS".
    61     02 FILLER     PIC X(26) VALUE SPACES.
    62 01 CAB-02.
    63     02 FILLER     PIC X(03)  VALUE SPACES.
    64     02 FILLER     PIC X(15) VALUE "NÚMERO DO SÓCIO".
    65     02 FILLER     PIC X(06) VALUE SPACES.
    66     02 FILLER     PIC X(13) VALUE "NOME DO SÓCIO".
    67     02 FILLER     PIC X(15) VALUE SPACES.
    68     02 FILLER     PIC X(18) VALUE "VALOR DO PAGAMENTO".
    69     02 FILLER     PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
    70     02 FILLER     PIC X(80) VALUE SPACES.
    71 01 DETALHE.
    72     02 FILLER         PIC X(06) VALUE SPACES.
    73     02 NUMERO-SOCIO   PIC 999.999.
    74     02 FILLER         PIC X(12) VALUE SPACES.
    75     02 NOME-SOCIO     PIC X(30).
    76     02 FILLER         PIC X(01) VALUE SPACES.
    77     02 VALOR-PAGO     PIC ZZZ.ZZZ.ZZ9,99.
    78     02 FILLER         PIC X(14) VALUE SPACES.
    79
    80 01 RODA-1.
    81     02 FILLER        PIC X(03) VALUE SPACES.
    82     02 FILLER        PIC X(26)
    83                       VALUE "Total de Sócios atrasados:".
    84     02 TOTAL-SOCIO   PIC ZZZZ9.
    85 01 RODA-2.
    86     02 FILLER        PIC X(03) VALUE SPACES.
    87     02 FILLER        PIC X(27)
    88                         VALUE "Valor Total atrasado     : ".
    89     02 TOTAL-VALOR  PIC ZZZ.ZZZ.ZZZ.ZZ9,99.
    90 PROCEDURE        DIVISION.
    91
    92 PGM.
    93     PERFORM INICIO.
    94     PERFORM PRINCIPAL
    95       UNTIL FIM-ARQ EQUAL "SIM".
    96     PERFORM TERMINO
    97     STOP RUN.
    98 INICIO.
    99     OPEN INPUT CADSOC1
   100          OUTPUT CADSOC2 RELSOCIO.
   101     PERFORM LEITURA.
   102
   103     LEITURA.
   104         READ CADSOC1
   105            AT END
   106            PERFORM RODAPE
   107            MOVE "SIM" TO FIM-ARQ.
   108 PRINCIPAL.
   109     PERFORM IMPRESSAO.
   110     PERFORM LEITURA.
   111
   112 IMPRESSAO.
   113     IF CODIGOPAGAMENTO1 EQUAL 01 THEN
   114         PERFORM VALIDO
   115     ELSE
* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 24-Apr-25 22:01 Page   3
*                                      EXERC1.CBL
   116        PERFORM INVALIDO
   117     END-IF.
   118 VALIDO.
   119     MOVE NUMEROSOCIO1 TO NUMERO-SOCIO2.
   120     MOVE NOMESOCIO1 TO NOME-SOCIO2.
   121     MOVE VALORPAGAMENTO1 TO VALOR-PAGAMENTO2.
   122     WRITE REG-SAI.
   123 INVALIDO.
   124     IF CT-LIN GREATER THAN 29
   125         PERFORM CABECALHO
   126     END-IF.
   127     PERFORM DETALHES.
   128 CABECALHO.
   129     ADD 1         TO CT-PAG.
   130     MOVE CT-PAG   TO VAR-PAG.
   131     MOVE SPACES   TO REG-ATR.
   132     WRITE REG-ATR AFTER ADVANCING PAGE.
   133     WRITE REG-ATR FROM PAG AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE.
   134     WRITE REG-ATR FROM CAB-01 AFTER ADVANCING 2 LINES.
   135     WRITE REG-ATR FROM CAB-02 AFTER ADVANCING 2 LINES.
   136     MOVE ZEROES   TO CT-LIN.
   137 DETALHES.
   138     ADD 1 TO SOMA-SOCIO.
   139     ADD VALORPAGAMENTO1 TO SOMA-VALOR.
   140     MOVE NUMEROSOCIO1     TO NUMERO-SOCIO.
   141     MOVE NOMESOCIO1       TO NOME-SOCIO.
   142     MOVE VALORPAGAMENTO1  TO VALOR-PAGO.
   143     WRITE REG-ATR FROM DETALHE AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE.
   144     ADD 1         TO CT-LIN.
   145
   146 RODAPE.
   147     MOVE SOMA-SOCIO TO TOTAL-SOCIO.
   148     MOVE SOMA-VALOR TO TOTAL-VALOR.
   149     WRITE REG-ATR FROM RODA-1 AFTER ADVANCING 2 LINE.
   150     WRITE REG-ATR FROM RODA-2.
   151 TERMINO.
   152     CLOSE CADSOC1 CADSOC2 RELSOCIO.
